title: Lombardi’s Week 14 Reactions | GM Street (Ep. 363)
description:
The Vikings struggle on offense, the Dolphins shock the Patriots, Chicago stymies the Rams, and the Steelers slip up in Oakland, plus the weekly awards.


Hosts: Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier
